{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.1","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:1","prev_osis_id":"Jer.039.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">J\u00e9r\u00e9mie en libert\u00e9<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. J\u00e9 39:11-14. (Pr 27:8. Ps 137:5, 6.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La parole qui fut adress\u00e9e \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie de la part de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, apr\u00e8s que Nebuzaradan, chef des gardes, l\u2019eut renvoy\u00e9 de Rama. Quand il le fit chercher, J\u00e9r\u00e9mie \u00e9tait li\u00e9 de cha\u00eenes parmi tous les captifs de J\u00e9rusalem et de Juda qu\u2019on emmenait \u00e0 Babylone.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.2","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.39.18","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 39:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.39.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.2","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:2","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Le chef des gardes envoya chercher J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, et lui dit: L\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, a annonc\u00e9 ces malheurs contre ce lieu;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.3","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.3","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:3","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>l\u2019\u00c9ternel a fait venir et a ex\u00e9cut\u00e9 ce qu\u2019il avait dit, et ces choses vous sont arriv\u00e9es parce que vous avez p\u00e9ch\u00e9 contre l\u2019\u00c9ternel et que vous n\u2019avez pas \u00e9cout\u00e9 sa voix.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.4","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.2","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.4","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:4","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Maintenant voici, je te d\u00e9livre aujourd\u2019hui des cha\u00eenes que tu as aux mains; si tu veux venir avec moi \u00e0 Babylone, viens, j\u2019aurai soin de toi; si cela te d\u00e9pla\u00eet de venir avec moi \u00e0 Babylone, ne viens pas; regarde, tout le pays est devant toi, va o\u00f9 il te semblera bon et convenable d\u2019aller.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.3","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.5","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:5","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Et comme il tardait \u00e0 r\u00e9pondre: Retourne, ajouta-t-il, vers Guedalia, fils d\u2019Achikam, fils de Schaphan, que le roi de Babylone a \u00e9tabli sur les villes de Juda, et reste avec lui parmi le peuple; ou bien, va partout o\u00f9 il te conviendra d\u2019aller. Le chef des gardes lui donna des vivres et des pr\u00e9sents, et le cong\u00e9dia.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.6","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.4","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.6","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:6","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie alla vers Guedalia, fils d\u2019Achikam, \u00e0 Mitspa, et il resta avec lui parmi le peuple qui \u00e9tait demeur\u00e9 dans le pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.7","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.7","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:7","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Guedalia gouverneur du pays de Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-16: cf. J\u00e9 41:1-15. Pr 28:12; 29:10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Lorsque tous les chefs des troupes qui \u00e9taient dans les campagnes eurent appris, eux et leurs hommes, que le roi de Babylone avait \u00e9tabli gouverneur du pays Guedalia, fils d\u2019Achikam, et qu\u2019il lui avait confi\u00e9 les hommes, les femmes, les enfants, et ceux des pauvres du pays qu\u2019on n\u2019avait pas emmen\u00e9s captifs \u00e0 Babylone,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.8","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.6","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.8","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:8","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>ils se rendirent aupr\u00e8s de Guedalia \u00e0 Mitspa, savoir Isma\u00ebl, fils de Nethania, Jochanan et Jonathan, fils de Kar\u00e9ach, Seraja, fils de Thanhumeth, les fils d\u2019\u00c9pha\u00ef de Nethopha, et Jezania, fils du Maacatite, eux et leurs hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.9","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.7","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.9","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:9","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Guedalia, fils d\u2019Achikam, fils de Schaphan, leur jura, \u00e0 eux et \u00e0 leurs hommes, en disant: Ne craignez pas de servir les Chald\u00e9ens; demeurez dans le pays, servez le roi de Babylone, et vous vous en trouverez bien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.10","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.8","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.10","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:10","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Voici, je reste \u00e0 Mitspa, pour \u00eatre pr\u00e9sent devant les Chald\u00e9ens qui viendront vers nous; et vous, faites la r\u00e9colte du vin, des fruits d\u2019\u00e9t\u00e9 et de l\u2019huile, mettez-les dans vos vases, et demeurez dans vos villes que vous occupez.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.11","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.9","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.11","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:11","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Tous les Juifs qui \u00e9taient au pays de Moab, chez les Ammonites, au pays d\u2019\u00c9dom, et dans tous les pays, apprirent que le roi de Babylone avait laiss\u00e9 un reste dans Juda, et qu\u2019il leur avait donn\u00e9 pour gouverneur Guedalia, fils d\u2019Achikam, fils de Schaphan.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.12","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.10","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.12","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:12","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Et tous les Juifs revinrent de tous les lieux o\u00f9 ils \u00e9taient dispers\u00e9s, ils se rendirent dans le pays de Juda vers Guedalia \u00e0 Mitspa, et ils firent une abondante r\u00e9colte de vin et de fruits d\u2019\u00e9t\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.11","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.13","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:13","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Jochanan, fils de Kar\u00e9ach, et tous les chefs des troupes qui \u00e9taient dans les campagnes, vinrent aupr\u00e8s de Guedalia \u00e0 Mitspa,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.14","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.12","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.14","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:14","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>et lui dirent: Sais-tu que Baalis, roi des Ammonites, a charg\u00e9 Isma\u00ebl, fils de Nethania, de t\u2019\u00f4ter la vie? Mais Guedalia, fils d\u2019Achikam, ne les crut point.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.15","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.15","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:15","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.040.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Et Jochanan, fils de Kar\u00e9ach, dit secr\u00e8tement \u00e0 Guedalia \u00e0 Mitspa: Permets que j\u2019aille tuer Isma\u00ebl, fils de Nethania. Personne ne le saura. Pourquoi t\u2019\u00f4terait-il la vie? Pourquoi tous ceux de Juda rassembl\u00e9s aupr\u00e8s de toi se disperseraient-ils, et le reste de Juda p\u00e9rirait-il?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.16","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.14","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.16","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:16","prev_osis_id":"Jer.040.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.041.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.40.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Guedalia, fils d\u2019Achikam, r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 Jochanan, fils de Kar\u00e9ach: Ne fais pas cela; car ce que tu dis sur Isma\u00ebl est faux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.40","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.41.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 41:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.41.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.40.15","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 40:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.40.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc1e0fb04.49343307');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc1e0fb04.49343307\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc1e0fb04.49343307","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc1e0fb04.49343307'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc1e0fb04.49343307\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}